---
import ServicePage from '../../components/ServicePage.astro';
---
<ServicePage
	title="in Clapham"
	highlight="Physiotherapy Prescribing"
	heroSubtitle="Medication can be an important part of rehabilitation — when used appropriately. Independent prescribing lets us reduce pain so movement-based treatment can work."
	breadcrumb="Physiotherapy Prescribing"
	seoTitle="Physiotherapy Prescribing in Clapham"
	seoDescription="Independent physiotherapy prescribing in Clapham. Medication reviewed and prescribed alongside rehabilitation to reduce pain and support recovery."
	intro={[
		"Medication can be an important part of rehabilitation — when used appropriately. At Balance, independent prescribing allows us to reduce pain and inflammation so that physiotherapy and movement-based treatment can be effective.",
		"The aim is not to rely on medication, but to create a window where we can reduce the pain so that you can move, exercise, and recover.",
	]}
	introImage="/physiotherapy-prescribing/treatment-rooms.jpg"
	whenHeading="When prescribing"
	whenHighlight="may be appropriate"
	whenIntro="You may benefit from this service if you:"
	whenList={[
		"Have pain levels preventing movement or exercise",
		"Experience acute back or neck pain",
		"Have significant post-operative pain limiting rehabilitation",
		"Experience nerve-related symptoms such as burning, tingling, or shooting pain",
		"Are not responding to over-the-counter medication",
		"Need support managing or reviewing current medication",
	]}
	whenImage="/physiotherapy-prescribing/reception.jpg"
	howHeading="How we"
	howHighlight="work"
	howIntro="Our approach prioritises using the minimum effective support, with a clear plan to reduce reliance on medication as your condition improves."
	howList={[
		"Clinical assessment of your condition",
		"Review of current medications and response",
		"Prescribing within scope of practice",
		"Clear guidance on dosage, duration, and expected effect",
		"Integration with physiotherapy and exercise-based treatment",
	]}
	howImage="/physiotherapy-prescribing/screenshot.webp"
	whoHeading="Who we"
	whoHighlight="help"
	whoList={[
		"People with acute spinal pain",
		"Post-operative patients",
		"Individuals with severe pain",
		"Patients with nerve pain",
		"Time-sensitive cases needing rapid support",
	]}
	whoImage="/physiotherapy-prescribing/front-entrance.jpg"
	faqs={[
		{ q: "What is an independent prescriber?", a: "A clinician trained to assess, diagnose, and prescribe medication within their area of expertise." },
		{ q: "Do I still need to see my GP?", a: "Not always for musculoskeletal issues, though we recommend keeping your GP informed." },
		{ q: "Is medication always necessary?", a: "No. It is used only when it will support your rehabilitation." },
		{ q: "Can this help with severe back or neck pain?", a: "Yes. Reducing pain can allow earlier movement and treatment." },
		{ q: "Will I stay on medication long-term?", a: "The aim is to reduce and stop medication as your condition improves." },
	]}
/>
